{"tid":334030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【畫足32年終收檔　微軟擬踢走「小畫家」","createTime":"2017-07-24T11:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T12:16:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"065b9ac4c230822e098c5b7ccd2d4cb31e8e593a","tid":334030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"小畫家？我細細個聽過呢個名喇！小學生電腦堂，總會用過佢畫畫吧？有得畫，好畫喇，微軟今日宣佈 Window 10 秋季更新將會踢走「小畫家」～<br />\n<br />\n自 1985 年 Window 1.0 的年代，小畫家已經是預載的繪畫及圖片編輯程式，時至 Window 10 小畫家都與微軟攜手同行。直至今年四月，微軟公佈 Window 10 的小畫家由「小畫家3D」（Paint 3D）取代；而今日微軟再宣佈，今年秋季更新將會「棄用」小畫家，意味著微軟將不用發展「小畫家」，可見的將來甚至會被正式移除。<br />\n<br />\n「小畫家」在 1985 年 11 月出世，雖然它一定不是畫畫最靚的程式，但幾乎人人用過，甚至是好多人第一個接觸的繪畫程式。當年初初出世，它只能處理 1-bit 的圖像。來到 Window 3.0，「小畫家」開始支援彩色，並重新設計用家介面。其後 Window 95，「小畫家」都繼續有更新，來到 Window 98、Window 2000 及 Window ME 用家更可儲存為 JPEG、GIF 及 PNG 檔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%99%A2-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4-%E7%95%AB%E8%B6%B332%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E6%94%B6%E6%AA%94-%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0-%E5%B0%8F%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%2599%25A2-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%2595%25AB%25E8%25B6%25B332%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%25AA%2594-%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=QwmHDIQMkF5p0IdhLXjCG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0a62fe8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%2599%25A2-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%2595%25AB%25E8%25B6%25B332%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%25AA%2594-%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=964e0fbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%99%A2-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4-%E7%95%AB%E8%B6%B332%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E6%94%B6%E6%AA%94-%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0-%E5%B0%8F%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6/</a>"},{"pid":"5ebd34f6283ee03e75cda8871f3718bb3a663c60","tid":334030,"uid":14103,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"我成日用佢黎快速save screen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d00587b4c12b2a2237bf3343589d6c9fbde4428","tid":334030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日用佢黎快速save screen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2<br />\n同埋整slide改圖勁好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03887e46f50cf15216ed7f56001b5e5d679abb","tid":334030,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"Window <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野垃圾報導"},{"pid":"8f3c6672bbdff10667cd408057d1de77f4c2b32d","tid":334030,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a82e21c767e7279899b01a926790f994688a06d7","tid":334030,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"IE都比M$自己淘汰咗(雖然edge都係廢)<br />\n咁小畫家要退休都好合理<br />\n唔該搵個好使好用嘅新野代替<br />\n唔好好似搵skype 代msn咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1897653400c7df760c523e5a2a4ce7e9b45df4e","tid":334030,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"